## Third Party Packages and Libraries
- Technical documentation is located in @docs/technical/00-libraries-packages.md
- When changes are made to either @pyproject.toml or @docs/technical/00-libraries-packages.md, ensure both files are in agreement.
- Whenever you add, remove, or change packages or libraries in [pyproject.toml](pyproject.toml), immediately run the following from the project root so the environment and linters stay synchronized: **activate the project virtual environment** (e.g. `source .venv/bin/activate`), then run `pip install -e ".[dev]"`
